      "comment": "ANSWERING (2) is due a winning run having placed second in three of his last four starts, including last time out over 1100m  at Mackay when beaten a head as the favourite after racing on the speed to the turn. Rates well as a leading chance. MISS MERCY (6) after placing in both of her previous runs finished sixth of 11 over 1000m at Sunshine Coast last start after racing on the speed to the turn. She drops 5kg in weight and from an inside draw looks well placed to return to top-three form. CANNY BE BETTER (3) ran a solid race when fresh-up from a spell last time out, finishing third of five over 1200m at Thangool. Trained here and having placed second of 10 here over today's distance last prep is worth an each-way ticket. KEYBOARD (1) lost ground after making a poor beginning, then came home well from the turn to finish second of five over 1100m at Emerald last start when sent out at long odds. Has won at long odds in the past and can fall into a place.",
